### Login
POST https://careerforge-hsmn.onrender.com/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "samannazir55@gmail.com",
  "password": "Haroon55"
}

### Create job (paste the accessToken from the login response above)
POST https://careerforge-hsmn.onrender.com/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "companyName": "Acme Corp",
  "jobTitle": "Backend Engineer",
  "status": "APPLIED"
}

### List jobs
GET https://careerforge-hsmn.onrender.com/api/jobs
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### Update job (replace JOB_ID)
PATCH https://careerforge-hsmn.onrender.com/api/jobs/JOB_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "INTERVIEW"
}

### Delete job
DELETE https://careerforge-hsmn.onrender.com/api/jobs/JOB_ID
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE